.com/a/ACg8ocKBJzzfu3_mwCUcQ1hqwSpOWPUZukwy8ayOv1md4R0BbapUOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a very janky outlet that was beyond our DIY abilities to repair. Isiah came out and was so helpful in explaining not just the outlet issue but giving a thorough overview of where our homes electric system was doing well / may need improvements. Nikolay came back the next day to handle the outlet repair and was friendly and efficient and did a thorough check after he completed work to make sure all was working perfectly. Was very happy with the work and everyone we engaged with was knowledgeable and professional!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angelica Rojas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1IVbaaIWNPiuER86_PB4IA0mUajBQcwG_9H955_qHXweoAcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience with this electric service provider today. They were professional, respectful, and took the time to clearly explain the issues without talking down to me (which unfortunately has happened with another company before, rhymes with Shmister Shmarky). They fixed our immediate problem and provided reasonable, transparent quotes for some upcoming upgrades we’ll need. Overall, a smooth and refreshing experience. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Lamoreux","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2SENwAWUD191o3R-vUqXUQVsQofo0Ilrc4POpA3WyLgUT7uE4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Trutec. Nikolay, Cole, and Alix were very friendly thorough and informative. They investigated and resolved most of my issues right during the consult and provided options for surge protection. The Trutec team were communicative with each other and seem to have great working relationships. I was pleased with the whole energy and will be using this service again in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sompop Phongen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaKTVdPbfWBvmEQolk9R2GBemyD9oK_HE__ijdxI0e4jof8-3P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Trutec Electric did amazing job on my driveway floodlight new installation. Isaiah very professional and provided good advice. I recommend Trutec if you need electrician assistance. I’m fully support family business in the neighborhood","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2BNzL0JsqCisGxhe1cheabD4ebvwbO7kaMuTOy9SDzPA1228KgSyaIH9VIHdxNf1pu7T3MFVivLjdq2GZTRn2KltiyITGxxrtipVE0V_5rWq1SHTEtdJWPYT5XjFsqniv_Z90zJfinBUVz=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-22"},{"Name":"aer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXLo0OzIsBXf3PWPO6ZbPZTTsqmg4YihAXcWnsD3I5VswOMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Contacted TruTec through a word-of-mouth recommendation, and they provided incredible service. Nikolay, Gabe and Hector worked extensively to identify and resolve the electrical outage in my home. They were all highly professional, thorough and considerate throughout the entire process. They took meticulous care to be sure the issue was resolved and provided clear communication each step of the way. It was an absolute pleasure to work with TruTec. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
