edgeable and the job looks great. I highly recommend this shop.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1yXGdFMPF5EblDchD58INq6wL9ePYN0_MMTThWzDd2i89sJhu-lDEmiO5xixE-zZcfplG7FnibhsM3uYhWHQBIGDDWyza-QOpZY4_BWdVcFFiy-dLXHraZOz4wWjZ23d-K1WhSeHmSde_F=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-6"},{"Name":"Conrad Prusak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJF4pENMQGDMMbuZob9nIUcpFJUrM0xq6A5cTV7XunQW2L0XQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Compliments to the ATX team. We just completed a challenging job. Lisa (owner) and John (very experienced field tech) both take their professionalism very seriously. They will work hard for you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"boydta1","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZ3eoAzNW8hADNZGJSO5sUPou9G5S3sHd7OmRmRNU72mUtJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"ATX to the rescue again!  One of our GCFI failed to the point of no return Saturday night / Sunday morning.  Due to that, none of the outlets in the restrooms had power.  Reached out to ATX (my go-to electricians) to schedule a repair. Since it was Sunday, i did not think i would get an appointment before Tuesday.  Well, John arrived before noon on Sunday and completed the repair (plus an upgrade) in under an hour.  Nice!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXq6H0kChVwtucAl19UAZUzjtEQlGiw6IJsBeLP1Woe3ydMzhA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John came to my home to fix several electrical outlets.  He did a great job.  He fixed the lights in the ceiling fan.  He noticed a light bulb needed replacing in the hall ceiling.  He checked all of the breakers in the breaker box.  He explained to me how the GFCI outlets work.  Then he helped me with putting together a dog crate for my rescue dog that I'm adopting.  He is a super nice guy.   He and his wife are foster parents of dogs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-c