t, and precise. His knowledge and attention to detail really showed.\n\nI highly recommend Asahel and the team at Terrapin.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kenny Leddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb5_AdFC25Q0Gqcig5L_VBmJA6Qx4ct0nfsrJJhYmJKLJU_A5FVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Roger came to do a same day install of our ring camera pro which required new 24V wiring  to replace a previous low voltage doorbell. He was quick, kind, professional and asked questions along the way to make sure that the end result was exactly how I was hoping for. Thanks!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0WI-C8nQKSekQhEvpG_2-hhqcbr-jCAXgjT7m4dt2JncbC8KsN_CHLUVOlk1DQJ38KzIRFUA1I66WWQiQfciSQqc4vn6pEMbRFAvmR0CrnabQW9tE2BYFrfMlFA4abnVLi-OiWlqvSpoiu=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-17"},{"Name":"Krista Larsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0VS4nBt9Dkh1BL8RodjfRjLYhW5YxC3WJTNhbfJCmpW3pxFGq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend Terrapin !! Needed an outlet installed in our bathroom and found them on Thumbtack. Scheduling was a breeze- they were able to have a tech come out a couple days later for a quote, which was A LOT better than the other quotes I’d received for this project. The tech Asahel was super great - knowledgeable and SO fast. Great experience overall!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Pelage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhiF_gUdx_ZheUjumyeSVuCJBo4q6BKVPSsMO1k2hHmhU8rcs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of working with Andres  from Terrapin Electric, and the experience was truly exceptional. From start to finish, Andres embodied the highest level of professionalism, technical mastery, and customer-first focus—easily making this the best service experience I've had in years.\nAndres's professionalism is unmatched. He arrived promptly, communicated clearly about the scope of work, and maintained a focused, respectful demeanor throughout the job. He treated my home with care and ensured the work area was clean and tidy before leaving.\n\nFinally, Andres’s commitment to high-end customer service and quality assurance is what sets him apart. He went above and beyond to double-check his work, offering clear assurance that the installation met all safety standards and would perform reliably. He made sure I was completely satisfied with every detail before considering the job finished.\n\nIf you are looking for an electrician who combines deep technical skill with outstanding courtesy and reliability, look no further than Andres. He is a tremendous asset to the Terrapin Electric team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"marcus geisler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqtYNhGRuirNixTA89YwyT2PBsgDB-MxSM1rKWmH4UKc7keg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic job by Andres from TerrapinElectric. He got here right on time, quickly diagnosed a bad switch and finishing the work  all in about 30-40 minutes. Took time to educate me about the repair and as well as the type of light bulbs I should use for the fixture. Thank you for your hard work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jourdan Labonte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVU61Ke0dsSbgd99YOaQQatG0RAC-WDO2-4ioXGCgubkO8in6hGKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Terrapin installed a 50 amp outlet and 140 kV whole home surge protector for my home. The staff were friendly and experienced, and I was satisfied with the installation. Great company to work with!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
