u you've never felt really confident with your electrician- Call Magnify. They are so friendly and professional and super knowledgeable. I had Taylor out at our house for a full days work and he was the best. Thoughtful and helpful with questions and did expert work for us. It brings me great comfort having found this super solid company and really seems to have the customers needs foremost in mind.  Give them a try for big or small electrical needs. I am now a devoted customer. Thank You Magnify and Taylor!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Sinishta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVle0L6b8b-Kdv11hCXGbEWzOdjZ8D_yL3fdI9fd33orx8nd5c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Christian was fantastic to work with. He repaired our bathroom fan by replacing the motor and optimizing the power, and the difference is night and day. He was punctual, professional, and clearly knowledgeable—he explained what needed to be done, completed the work efficiently, and made sure everything was running perfectly before he left.\nIt’s rare to find someone who combines technical skill with great customer service, but Christian absolutely does. We’ll definitely call Magnify Electric again for any future electrical needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Benjamin Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSuNCUfL437MYuAbslXDle72wKiYsoklgxxDIRJU-Aqdnd2ZE_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Taylor is the real deal. He’s a highly skilled electrician, punctual, responsible, professional, and extremely thorough in his work. I reached out to several companies for quotes, and Magnify Electric was by far the most responsive. Exceptional service from start to finish. I highly recommend them to anyone in Austin!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria Schmidt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLS8NbFnjKLT80tO4n6cJyk5zMv_6zcW3FoRgCPgRiMtgCG5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Craig to help us with some breakers in our house and he was incredibly kind, efficient, respectful, and had everything he needed to fix the issue! We appreciated his candor and loved that he gave us options regarding how we wanted it done. Once he was finished, everything worked flawlessly and we haven’t had any problems since. We are so grateful for him \u0026 will be using Magnify Electric in the future!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Ireland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVU_oYAvvq3hCFpxzUf72AbCvVVZBdtGc5rSlkUELUM7-7iYL8n=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Magnify Electric is Electric!!!! First time utilizing their services and it was an all around fantastic experience. Felicia was so helpful and kind, the epitome of amazing customer service!! Tayler was wonderful as well, he was prompt and explained everything. We were given two options for the lighting repairs, which was not expected, but greatly appreciated! Will be utilizing them for any future electrical work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joshua Lucas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLM-XGg6QWgUhpzS-BHwDUpsUDi4qqeTuOV8HBoWAgdQzHS7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The guys were professional, friendly and did excellent looking work! They set up a new panel for a sauna, and took the time to make the control connections and make sure everything started up. We've used Magnify a few times and highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas LaBoube","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTNFNkLXdwiJpRirOdqi9c0hfIYcNLJAvD5hsob8yHgoOW3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Garage power issue quickly resolved. The electrician was courteous and professional. Diagnosed the problem quickly and fixed it immediately.  I have used Magnify before and have always been well pleased. Real professionals at reasonable prices.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extend