ull,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Ginsel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYtNAT5vyLlCcP9Sy_yibVQq3dl-VEyFPPy8ALnSfMVPSGKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding service.\nCorey installed all new breakers in my outside panel ( 26 years old  breakers)  and added extra outlets in my garage for convenience.\nGreat communication,  and doesn't mind working later at night if you work all day.\nI WILL HAVE MORE WORK FOR HIM !!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Travis Stucki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_SumvdZURPfTRx2layPKmqBqRi1Rn9VQHZHDlRiuStiaATBjZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This review is long overdue.   We hired Corey to install under counter lighting and also add a permanent light in our under stairs pantry and also added track lighting into our media room.  The pictures don't do it justice.  Corey came in and did a great job explaining everything he was doing and did the job in just a day and a half.  He also installed extra outlets.  We couldn't be happier with his work.  We highly recommend Corey and hope to use him for future projects.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37n7zMXdsQgBRjgzsYyig4xJt1BDM6dYG50iNBANQaPq3r2D0-Xe1H6oYRttVXJWd8LhLGr-GoTnEfMwzSYCF5DrFSBl3MxW_BmJgWj4vkxAVCh71r0BuAMMe7cifBnd6N0TC4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2MkqjuZORzTFjt8gjrgv73WQxBAtSx84M7EG67usrhl41JjpItfy-FTKfWPBJXNlKIAMpE5gM0UvtvHBkK_UubAPR_xdo5GlNv0VzWKB-vi_m5_dRWjL30Rti0gzbty3UlXvN2Dg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1EJ9r6yZyO6Qf0DXsC25bquNKrTKC4r23usuv-LT6207SBklNyWyjgxLqK1krvmGECVELYtLjjbYbaOEIWLkA0HRACUbwOCXr9DIFZx33dnk4RSjTnaf0lZfKigSGZ_1ytB62s=k-no"],"When":"2021-11-4"},{"Name":"Jim Magill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtcn_6Y0oYzJwrspqmQ3IfqZkzX2qiaP_yh35CpqDrwb00ThWV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely thrilled with the service from Corey at Nealco Electrical Services! From the start, Corey was an outstanding communicator—clear, responsive, and always kept me updated every step of the way. What really stood out was his dedication: he worked late into the night two nights in a row just to ensure the job was completed on time. His professionalism, attention to detail, and commitment to getting it done right were truly impressive. If you're looking for someone dependable, skilled, and easy to work with, I highly recommend Corey and the team at Nealco Electrical Services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Calo C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOxEfl0OkkUgTsRYeR0bQkCEWFgw0PDNBbcTA5x_BXmG6hiV2uFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I reached out to Corey about my breaker tripping. He responded within the hour, asking for a picture to confirm the style I had. He had the exact breaker I needed on hand and was able to squeeze me in that afternoon.\nHe did a great job explaining the issue and swapped it out in less than 10 mins.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1cgmml3ODoJt5Da10RhK0By9762KS58keqbTwoEpO6zUg0cqgSU7G6-rtaA4yRvplk1WzLyWNU3aMX_hcvZkFF-uWDg96YZ82ja2aNXPvA907mfM1J-TUyQ0MTfpHcmjxpr9Bd=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22hsCl10uy8Rp62j578Sxd_kIiJyGMSXVfwyWOc57Pw-ttz9dlefxcaJJrwSnhh2wWJWQAlGcqDPQ_X0ZnCPMZobiPbB7t9Y--Y7H77w13NYTKWuxXuGzfjGdsIz77BQoMAJBw=k-no"],"When":"2023-5-15"},{"Name":"Michele Bisciglia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4EGra2KvZkNKQCqJLWr_xIHnDl5iZGCNYRjCfro99TffDfmM4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Corey installed a new breaker for us and answered all of our questions about why we were experiencing tripping issues. While doing so, he looked over our panel setup and recommended certain upgrades - but not once did we feel like he was being dishonest and trying to get us to make changes that weren't pertinent. We were very happy with his estimates and the quality of his work!\n\nHe's highly skilled and trustworthy and goes above and beyond to let you know he's got your back. We'll definitely recommend him to our friends!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mir Ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBm2H36a175GAQBfE7-M2Gg1Wf7flpTF0oViEb4UfJAeWTX2vf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Corey is an AMAZING electrician and you should hire him if you need ANY work done! He communicates quickly, is always on top of things, and gave me an amazing price on top of it all. I got a quote for a surge protector \u0026 a breaker and he beat all the nearby competitors easily. Next time I ever have a problem I will be calling Nealco and you should too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tyler Schoulte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8hcjeOUMJwikmvtND0Hg5Y2-iD7ZL_thaUtLIe_M1GP-BcttZbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I texted Corey Neal from Nealco Electrical Services, asking to install an EV charger in my garage. He was fast getting me a quote from some pictures I took, completed the install for a fair price, and did a quality job! When I raised a concern I had with the install, Corey was quick to take ownership and make things right without hesitation, and that meant a lot to me as a customer! Would hire again for any other electrical jobs!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
