t the electrician, Hayward, would be arriving soon. They also sent a pic, bio, and link to track his impending arrival. As a dog parent, this tracking information was very valuable. Hayward completed the job efficiently and thoroughly and was extremely easy to work with. Altogether, this was a positive experience, and we plan to use Colvin in the future.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
