 knowledgeable, and genuinely helpful — this is how service should be. Easily a 10/10. Highly recommend. You won’t be disappointed. Thanks Jason.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"G MRMB","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYql1ogbV97Z5VfoejgvroJB46nP9Wfw7PQ3xL68K0Pb_MtRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used Jason Hurley on projects at my home and have been very pleased with his quality, honesty, pricing and integrity. There is significant construction in my neighborhood in addition to freeway construction which are all causing power outages. When the power is restored we experience surges that have cost us a small fortune in appliance repairs and replacements. Jason recently installed a solution for us - a home surge protector which we are so grateful for because we have not experienced any additional catastrophes since he installed it. We’ve lived in our home for 30 years and have been through many service professionals and we consider Hurley Electrical Services one of the best and the only electrician we will use.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emily Good","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUj1BIHjFBnNI_KZ-yCRpn0fUlFxOO6h1YAPC_bK_nNi03nCo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 would recommend Jason to anyone needing electrical services in ATX! He was an excellent communicator when scheduling, arrived early, did the job efficiently and cleaned up his workspace before leaving, which was greatly appreciated. Plus, he's wonderful to talk to! Thanks, Jason.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxgg5KbHTR9eEg1hCbZwXos69um9DLKlkDphAaW370bILaYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jason and his son were great to work with. Would absolutely recommend them for any electrical work. Very fair prices, great communication, and took the time to figure out the best solutions for our project. Will definitely be using them again in the future","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vikram Joglekar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfz7sOp2NSP6yUi2XvgRKFjtqhhKnKZZEkCh10zEvxCqC6ezFt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jason and Jake were great. Fixed a light switch for me and were very transparent about pricing, what their schedule was looking like, what time they would be over, what I should expect...everything!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peggy Ugent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqq46fpoljyH4fwWwfiZs-kIkTQ1hc0lq2SDa7MmTr0oxfYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have used Hurley’s Electrical for years and wouldn’t use anyone else.  Extremely responsive and professional, and reasonably priced.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Barbour","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmP5TsUuud-zJqOh5wB-wYQojfaBJ1SxDAHGhdgMO8Y4x4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got so lucky when Jason from Hurley's Electrical Services arrived to handle a wish list of lighting changes. We were concerned that our list might be too trivial and anxious that a big brand company wouldn't prioritize our project. So when we asked our neighbors for a recommendation and read the reviews about Jason we gave him a call. He was at our home promptly, taught us not just about what he was doing by also why, and charged a very fair price. We liked him so much we kept adding other ideas to our list.\nChoosing an electrician can feel like a leap of faith. You trust that the person assigned to your project has the expertise to do the job and the smarts to anticipate how this one electrical change will impact the rest of the wiring in your home. If you've ever hired a big brand to do this work, have you ever worried that you might be the training ground for a high-turnover team? We all want safe circuits in our homes. Hurley's Electrical Services delivers outstanding service, up-to-date expertise and priceless peace of mind.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
