d use them again for electrical work with no hesitation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DONNA VAWTER","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKx6aj-sAyOurxmnisSK5wjFwsZ_Qx4uBesNW-MDS-Ix5VO0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We called DeNucci Electric in the morning and they had a technician out that afternoon!  Alex did a great job resolving all of our electrical issues, stayed until almost dark getting everything accessed and repaired in a remodel we are doing. Great customer service, polite friendly and best of all a great price for the job! We will definitely use DeNucci Electric for all of our future projects! Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
