vey Electric! They were so nice and quickly got us on the schedule for hanging a chandelier we were unable to do ourselves due to 20 foor ceiling. They were on time, friendly and affordable. I would not hesitate to call them again and I wished I had called them sooner. My entryway is now as updated as the rest of our house:)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJPeWSbSAAnMiXERPqQ3YpYDwlA12yecoBLgwZkPcoJui7Rw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience using these guys. Scheduling was easy, called them on a Friday and they had someone out Monday morning! Team was excellent! They did a fantastic job of explaining their plan ahead of time and filled us in on any additional details throughout the process. They spent their time isolating the issue to a specific light, replaced it and everything is working now! A++++ Highly recommend and would use their service again!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelley Helms","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURh8On-Bg4rgDwtifv6AQCtE6iRs6VioYg8LFx3_10-f0CotQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a great experience! I have had HEI do quite a bit of work for me…hot tub hook up (2x), recessed lights, outlet installs, power for an electric range and then a gas range, adding breakers, etc.. They are professional, timely, very reasonable and a pleasure to do business with. Highly Recommend!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rich Hoops","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJal_v_aM5XJgB1KH34dG5GG7ROd98u7amJDMZ9NUq3n0335w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's hard to find amazing service and honesty these days. This service provides both. Don't hesitate to contact them. Friendly people too. They could have quoted me a lot of money. They did not. They were as honest as can be. Thank you Harvey Electric.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Wagner","ProfilePictu