 Baylee and his team were fast, efficient and professional. They came for a quote on Friday and we had everything done on Wednesday in a few hours. They were flexible and worked with our busy schedules.\n\nThank god for their safety check during our estimate session. They found a couple of things our builder got wrong that would have caused major problems in the future.\n\nCost was reasonable and the team respectful of schedules. Will be coming back next time we need anything!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Rooni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhE5vXryQELz_weF5ClXUhXDkUEa3pEzz984l2g3bt73Rtnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lane Amidon did a great job installing my EV Home Charging Station. Lane was courteous, expedient, and very professional. He really knew his stuff. I will be calling on Lane and Tejas Electric for all of my future electric service needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Cunningham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrtYKcWmrRHzX5v-TILoP4b0w3kSSLdEP4LNS8GF61SV3bP96x=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tejas Electric and Baylee Owen did an exceptional job running power to our backyard sauna. They were extremely thorough, and even went as far as mounting the heater after running power.  Overall a phenomenal experience - I will definitely call them again for future projects and couldn’t recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Holt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYK1T6kOVSVtueFB1MSmAAy2TEIArXZI0LjX2ZMYTA11__Zg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have worked with Tejas Electric for several years and I highly recommend them.   They are reliable, honest, and very professional.  Two of their employees, Baylee and Logan, performed some electrical work at my house yesterday.  Later that evening, a separate electrical issue unrelated to the work they had done popped up.  I called Tejas Electric at 8am today and both Baylee and Logan were at my house within an hour.  They quickly identified and resolved the issue, an aged and faulty switch,  performed a thorough inspection of my electrical system, allayed any concerns on my part, and made simple suggestions to improve the functionality of my system.  Baylee and Logan were both polite, professional, very good at their jobs, and a pleasure to work with.  I highly recommend Tejas Electric!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jan-Michael Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4udOStEZwJmjvsYJ_9r_ZuvRa8HS2BPuuy_bMuo6uj1TCWpZPSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a fantastic experience with Tejas Electric. Baylee and Logan (the apprentice) came out to handle a tricky job involving our 14-foot kitchen ceilings. They didn't just fix the dark lights; they successfully extended the circuit so all 9 recessed lights finally work on our single Lutron smart dimmer, which is a huge functional upgrade for the room.\n\nThey also installed a Vortexx whole-home surge protector to keep our high-end appliances safe and even took a moment to verify the wire gauge for our EV charger while they had the panel open. They were professional, thorough, and took the time to explain the safety logic behind everything. Highly recommend this crew!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
