ht on my car—a job that is often much more complex and time-consuming than it sounds. I called them yesterday, and they were very helpful, telling me to stop by today for an estimate.\n\nThe owner was incredibly friendly and transparent. After getting the estimate, I asked about scheduling the work. He told me that if I left the car right then (around 11 AM), they would get it done before the end of the day. To my surprise and delight, they called me before 2 PM to let me know my car was ready!\n\nThe replacement was perfect, the service was unbelievably fast, and the final price was very reasonable. This team is highly professional, efficient, and super friendly. If you're in the Austin area and need quality work, look no further than All Points Mechanics!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chase Aldredge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYlj97BbLWoXh_GRam_Pk8wibgEWGvzXXyRVj6O1GAFZs3vJ6D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Let me tell you, Eddie and his crew are fantastic! I had issues with another shop wiring up my truck wrong and melting the wiring harness and blowing fuses. They installed TEQ customs headlights to my 2001 Tacoma and also LED tail lights along with fixing the wiring issues the other shop had done. Eddie was super professional and got the job done right. Really cool down to earth dude. They did an amazing job! I’m going back to them to get my bumper and light bars installed soon. Trust me even if you live across the city it’s worth the drive!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3FEJCiuGTofjOidPtH1e1egmtRnmFitrf9wBBLj2z2ZPp9gxO41NZbEOqI3eZc84m3CgUR7BNJfyK6-0Cq97yb7BbDqVZmb5Amj99IocCOYb0ezm6J4rf1ntmvkNXZCGe-Fy189PzGgWs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3fWc8cRART1VwyxHYQSGL1Daonqw7GKLFQijEdWLrEEg1pjW7kMUdUtHR0uj2aTAYlZJehBSVJzqT97cajwIJEImNkXVgSa0iyvTg9bzXs7ep1gO91iljnd60EnP4cS6d_HOjzFbngtrJI=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-10"},{"Name":"Clayton Stemple","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfzVlNJ2vMooDK7Im0F9GDJbWL_k_7JX78vfCxX5q8fc9e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eddie from APAE does great work and provides wonderful customer service. Took my 2019Jeep Grand Cherokee to get maintenance service. Eddie got it done the same day without price markup or unnecessary service. He followed up the next day and following month to ensure my vehicle was running well. I highly reccomend Eddie and APAE for your automotive needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joshua Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfrUPI3XANhFuAO4yVXCMZHG_r3WaPxx8yY0wDoe6rhysEIfhk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I brought my car into Eddie and the team for the first time recently. I loved how they first tried to figure things out on the spot to see if they could send me on my way (find me a mechanic that tries to save you time and money!) but I ended up needing to leave it with them. They called me shortly after detailing what needed to be done. Turned the car around very quickly and were flexible with pick up. I also thought pricing was VERY reasonable - certainly below what the dealership wanted to charge (and what ChatGPT thought it would cost). I highly recommend All Points and I will definitely be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Advincula","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrbJ1nmaFqB2683PhqhqdcE6261-cEcfPKt0wDwrT9y3kNXAKU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eddie was great! Took care of my car through and through and I highly recommend for any of your car needs. I had an old Honda Civic 2014 and he was able to take care of it. Appreciate the care and attention you give to all your customers Eddie!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Van Loan II","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWknoYiylxYlQxzHIJ5fzDSDF66WLZpig5oNifjiWLsNo8q-sxUTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This shop really saved the day and got me back on the road!!\nI was having some electrical issues with my Infiniti M37 with the tech package (adaptive cruise control, intelligent brake assist, lane departure prevention, etc.) and the auto shop I had been going to for 6 years told me... “This is too complex for us, you’ll have to take your car to a place that really specializes in auto electronics.”\n\nLong story short, I had the car towed and I had to replace my ECM and entire wiring harness to get everything working perfectly again but All Points Auto Electric really took great care of the car, explained everything to me in detail, and did an amazing job! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Knopf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJAfCi6_wgt9xF28mbjoKiztodT27obAdWwU6c1Dxoc8jsWcnp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They only needed one business day to diagnose my issue and replace the spark plugs and ignition coils.  Reasonable costs and great communication.  Arranged for me to pick up my key after business hours.  Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sophia Bautista","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3BGlMMhhwpNVxy2jlOqGhY3-1a5LtcSpELvbGDiUjw7KXkb54=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best auto experience I’ve had in this town. Every other auto shop I’ve been to up charges, isn’t straightforward about the work that needs to be done, and is RUDE. These guys were quick, extremely helpful, reasonably priced, and didn’t talk down to me. Definitely my go-to auto shop in town now!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
