een acting weird flashing on and off. A electrician from Austin Energy said there was corrosion in our meter can. Today Ray came out and waited for another Austin Energy to shot off the power so Ray of Bowne could replace the bad parts. He is now waiting for the power to be restore. We are delighted with how Bowne responded so quickly and for the excellent work they continue to do for us.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1oZ3hoZtlwoKDl1VVUzl9mzG8zhe8MrZlj35zykr4zQZ2qU-_4FcwAWLChL3PM8cZeNHykzlC1DLcX0LTldD81YxMpgWkOU0AL3JOTama9ExA-BShXqcQBuItfuVJIe4DYv_iZEQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jpJmpicVbCU3_m5leycglcPXzWc4ZTpyka-ClR0wzBYsZAT8nMp3WwNo9DWXZhd19K7xjFn7olLQJYpCnnwEIp1NwHP6NAyiEy1Rk8_3oj--PgWTbDnjnr-JcyzBE687lqIRF=k-no"],"When":"2023-3-23"},{"Name":"Krystle Blanchard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWh7r1Hd5niNDrZhNfdEg_CE_MHAeOLjr25Ic8QfFrHfg3pknUjBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have not used your company but I do believe that the people you have workqing for you represent you. With that being said I watched one of your vehicles leave a bar/restaurant and drive erratically.  Speeding, riding bumpers and on his phone. All in a 45 mph/under construction neighborhood.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mina Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDrqdOeDAq6hylksFnAe0jLnpc_6SiD297StIJbDdV1C1YaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have hired at least three -- maybe four -- electricians since we bought our house four years ago for various issues. Our experience with Bowne has been SO GREAT, relative to any others. Their technicians really know what they are doing, they are excellent problem solvers, they schedule quickly and efficiently and come when they say they will. I was especially impressed with Ray, he is very pleasant and figured out how to wire and hang my exterior speakers which wasn't easy to do. AND they clean up after! So great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clint Compton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXocxlUcrMq988kJj1bfPCuWS3YTZTFr0ggpMqGjag9lVgXCz3LUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bowne is one of the most professional and high quality companies we've ever worked with. Every technician who came to work was friendly, qualified and completed the work to our satisfaction in a timely manner. We are so glad to have found Bowne and will continue using it for future needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ellis Doan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi5-1E8huvgu5-OGXBNwLlF66bosNqrf6Xgajn5kvdU9-rO298=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Far and away, Bowne electric has been the best electrical contractor I have used.  From large projects to a simple check on an electrical short circuit, they have by far been one of the most professional and prompt contractors that I know of.  When they say that they will show up at 0800 on a particular day, they will show up either on the dot or before 0800.  They have demonstrated again and again that they hire very competent, professional, and courteous employees.  I highly recommend them, and I will continue being a repeat customer should I need any electrical work in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Liebert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiwj5jtej3HZtXfBSM8mloM1FEUuEo6GX5dComeYR-mhzPLy7lGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I received 5 star service!  Erjon Manaj arrived when promised.  He efficiently found/fixed the problem with a light.  He explained what he found, and also explained how he was going to fix it.  He was professional, helpful, and prompt.  I highly recommend him!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debi Vanwey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtJTZA4PkrUQ9WNrMQaxi0baOaCPxGusuKCkCLTb-EgbnmWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adam and his crew replaced all of the flourescent lighting in our office building with LEDs, and also upgraded some of the wiring, as well as fixing one electrical problem.   They were kind, professional, courteous, and on time from beginning to end, and their work was exceptional.  They are experts in their field, and I give them the highest recommendation.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
