ion":"I had technicians came to fix my a/c. They installed a new disconnector breaker, but the a/c is still not working. So, I called Bear Electric and Scott came. He quickly found out one of the fuses was not working. Then he communicated the a/c folks very nicely and explained details. He also helped me to save money - a/c company willing to pay for Scott's invoice for me. Big help!! Thank you, Scott ！","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"CANYON CREEK DESIGN BUILD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQgU13Ozt2Lac1Tt1GJPHzPGdpURZz1X4wrWdyqNffgohRU-s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott installed our Generac a few years ago and did a great job.  It was time for our annual maintenance and Logan came out the next day to complete the service work.  Very professional, explained any issues, and make those corrections in a timely manner.  I highly recommend BEAR ELECTRIC!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gmail users","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiu4nvZ4ZiGdDANqPZDyz552yhdFHHgopCBibG-pEou-OmYnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently hired Bear Electric to install a whole house surge protector, and we were incredibly impressed with the service provided by Scott.\nFrom the start, Scott was exceptional. He arrived promptly, called ahead to confirm his arrival, and maintained a high level of professionalism throughout the entire appointment.\nWhat stood out most was his expertise. Scott clearly explained the function of the surge protector, where it would be installed, and patiently answered all of our questions about our existing electrical panel. He didn't just install the device; he educated us on the value of the investment, making us feel completely confident in the work.\nThe installation itself was quick, clean, and meticulous. Scott took great care to ensure the area around the panel was tidy both during and after the job. The final result looks perfectly integrated and safe.\nScott is a true professional—knowledgeable, thorough, and highly dependable. We highly recommend asking for Scott if you need any electrical work done, especially for a crucial safety feature like a whole house surge protector. Five stars for Scott and Bear Electric!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Marcincavage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlA03MFSQUNBFxbThxIUqBsdCwCb989iO0dBaSYECcrd73ww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bear Electric installed a whole house generator for me in March 2025.  This also involved extensive updates to my homes outdated service connections.  Scott explained all of the work in detail and provided a detailed estimate.  The work was completed on schedule with high quality and the generator performed flawlessly on the few occasions it was needed last year.  I recently contacted Bear to review the suggested annual maintenance on the system.  The work was promptly scheduled and completed per the quote.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Travis Nordgren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3U6IwUSN1dKdtMMuj82Yz5pcutXvbD_O16jnwcDo9wB21GQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experience with Bear Electric. Had an outdoor outlet go out Sat AM and was able to book a Monday appointment online. Scott called early Monday to talk through the issue and schedule repair. He was at the house within 45 minutes and handled the repair quickly and effectively, at a reasonable cost. Would highly recommend, top service all around. Very professional and personable. Thanks Scott!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRuTkNkKZUiPe-8E5jAyaIHWN4ZA2oueftKJRD6UVGvcpArrk8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very happy with the service we received from Bear Electric LLC. Their electrian was promptly on time, worked swiftly, and did great work. Getting a quote over the phone/ text was easy and our service request was scheduled and completed in no time. No surprises, competitive rates, and our project was completed just as we wanted it. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Collins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuPfi8rk__m0KIIRMo_HuFzegeSf0WFxE7CBsHz6lFlfp2og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with Bear and the team!  Arrived on time, did quality and quick work on an outlet addition needed in the attic. The electricians were nice to work with and all at a reasonable price.  Will use again for future needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUasu40sYVvdZJWW_oH1mNyvsWFP7cIwPdUAmKf2Pm4_kSXvC2R=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an EV charger install it was a great overall experience. They arrived on time, work was done quick and the charger worker perfectly. Would definitely call them again in the future for any issues I have with electrical work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
