7","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Sebastian Langguth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKyZi5u7p1j0sAsn0o4lZvpk27PTs1jjaMKw1zHk_NmujVlBmFXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the best electrician I’ve hired in NW Austin. The whole team knows what they’re doing and they never tried to upsell me on anything.\n\nThey installed a transfer panel for my generator, hardwired a hot tub, and took care of a few smaller fixes.\n\nI really appreciated how honest and straightforward they were. Overall, just a solid experience. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Parreno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6Sn4IMYDFDkAblFu2bYmfWyjHVwLy0VyNU7jGWGXWPYYmcTU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After noticing a poster billboard at a old grocery store in the Brentwood neighborhood of Austin\n\nAnd it just so happened. I needed to line up an electrician for this week to get some work done while my customer was out of town.\n\nI called the number and Shelby answered, I informed him what I needed to get done and asked for a general idea of cost, and offered to send some photos and measurements as potential clients often do with me,\n\nShelby gave me a ballpark and said his guys would be out there between 1-3 and they were there exactly at 3 o’clock two guys and right away I can tell they had experience and they were going to do quality work we confirmed the price and moved forward, and the project went extremely fast and clean and even after a third employee showed up, it was a smooth, great experience I’ve been around the trades for a little over 40 years and I’ve seen it all in every field\n\nThese guys are the top of their game I highly recommend them!  And their number is saved in my contacts for future!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3jsMYbSkYX2R408RTe4YZU09MwAHvXi1_JO7b8bIF1U5vv0TxFTCn_ZeT2pJEB8UNN6y