 replacing an old 2-prong outlet. Lance and Robert provided a quote. Robert and David performed the work. In both cases, the team was punctual, courteous, tidy, and professional. The did high-quality work--better than expected. (And hooray! They didn't try to upsell us! We live in a 1957 house, so tradespeople almost always try to upsell us.)\nWe are very pleased with the work. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Krueger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ3WjpQJtnKSGdLYRLuN3aQCmuDxQWa2Gr8ObBBumfRnI4nQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've had a few electricians work on my house over the years, and Klock's is my favorite. They are easy to work with and get the job done right. I'll be calling them next time I need some electrical work done, and will be recommending them to my neighbors.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary Cash DDS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWE5kOboJUsdSfC2nnpN8lYUwsXi8GNMTxIdBWxCbBi6Z1jEhGl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 stars!!\nI couldn't recommend Klocks enough!\nThe electrician Robert was courteous, punctual and efficient.\nI expected multiple days of electrical work and anticipated buying multiple fixtures but he was able to repair the problem without buying fixtures AND finished it in one day!\nHighly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
