ame as a referral. Just bought a new construction home that was slapped together with very basic electrical work. From the time we called Tino he came out within a few days. We walked through the house and he made his recommendations and then it wasn’t very long after we got a very reasonable estimate from what the others were estimating. To be honest even if we were quoted a little higher I would’ve paid it because I was so pleased with his customer service. We had ceiling fans installed, recessed lighting added to some of the rooms, and upgraded the lights over the island in the kitchen. Everything was done perfectly!! I highly recommend Tino!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2LPV5v-MnFBbJAM1umIPHwbvemqsEkly0qqOJim0m7LzVw2mpIUI175QLAStjRND9jNgQX8wqG5DE775S9xyW0rKgFeCT9PpxvlZiRyTWqqEV7NprYMhhk8N2dtb2kP0hwPOXu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qOzZiCqgj0KiD-aB0AvlWEkb6XkLrSr4F6xhdA9ZS2IsWWZZO2yWqXMKAlj-cyCtC9OsTJUp6CLRkf8FX3FOc_awxiOPcldQRCPmYL2StruS3kid8WT2NJ-x9_6OMMDZ6mVO0yA=k-no"],"When":"2022-1-23"},{"Name":"Clint Hormann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoLJpmXIa8TcdVZCQH54DdN0OHSZ5Ai0jZEvyrFMLO8cM3yoo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tino and his team did the landscape lighting at our home. Ran a dedicated line fully across the home through the attic. Trenched and hid wire throughout the yard. Looks absolutely stunning. Couldn’t be happier with his level of service and value for the money. I’ll be calling them for all my electrical work going forward.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1F8bozNQa5BFXhbtSif3hjpXjXXrwSgu303Of9-EKP_k4wXrFvy6ItFYVeJ80RhFaQtbmVvHMdaTWQBl6lrd2KKu_IvZqW-VwnSc62e8JcDaivEs05O7Uosj0u8g9m4RVR7ZHm=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn37ZOID0Rzo5-TRj8IshLIMOhkOp7h5CkKtTZRYT3LkfX4yQ-JWwgsJ5gwmX2UdzcF4NwOSjJuP1dK-1z7SeJ1jvJefPQ5TQl7P2JwHIPsgKt-MnvKmqr0gQ2z6xcvvYdRbEdyU=k-no"],"When":"2023-9-12"},{"Name