RfqA3f8tRF8XP4V7JZscx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1QxkmYXKYzzxZC0Tvl5Zl2dVHA05H2xORDN66tN9v53HX50xIUJ2bczBBCudXA-Mnd_QR-UqjD-pmRB3lToYGgoC_FRoXP-R5AQD6g_AVoilcgkH-sYP5emuMyjsKzoY8t0IlWe-LBprQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-20"},{"Name":"Linda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKE3_9yds50CPB8px-QbKJ5RE6IQRBxcOPyPb5UyJDqM35TTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent! Excellent!! Excellent!!!\nTodd and Leo were true professionals from start to finish.  I was able to get an appointment that worked for me, they showed up on time, and ready to get to work.  There were many electrical jobs to complete in the house (old house that was just purchased) and all were done with attention to detail and they took the time to explain each job.  Their pricing was very fair.   Thank you so much Todd and Leo!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maryam Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMOWv8whJriTzFWA-Rj95meLIixt4zdFqSQbfPnDRueYV4QbLc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Todd worked on multiple electrical projects (including rebuilding of outdoor panel, GFCI installation, light installation and adding a new 30A receptacle to my garage) at my house and I was impressed by his professionalism and expertise.\n\nTodd was prompt in his response and arrived at our property on time. He took the time to thoroughly assess our needs, providing a quote that was reasonable, fair and transparent. Todd offered valuable insights and suggestions that helped us avoid unnecessary work that our home inspector had recommended, such as upgrading to AFCI, installing a ground conductor or grounding the gas supply meter. For each of these items, Todd showed us why the existing installation was sufficient for safety.\n\nWhen it came time to execute the job, Todd's attention to detail was excellent. He worked diligently to ensure everything was done cleanly, just as he had set out on the project quote. Throughout the project, Todd was always willing to address any questions or concerns we had, demonstrating his commitment to customer satisfaction.\n\nOverall, I can't recommend Todd highly enough. His professionalism, fairness, and dedication to his craft make him a standout electrician in my book. If you're looking for someone reliable and skilled for your electrical needs, Todd is definitely the one to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Billings","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmMjgh12GQYP1uyJnaKuG4fKbvrkyIu94uKDYa7IMa6BT8Aggjog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We highly recommend Tomei Electric. Todd and Leo were able to sneak us into their schedule quickly (Todd was very communicative on availability/timing), they did a fantastic job installing a receptacle in the attic, and were fairly priced. We will certainly be using Tomei Electric again for any future needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"joel salman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfHeaudBUzYKRn7qPo8emBF9TOec4dhqfMXAbsHvYPSkm9ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent!  Quality work at reasonable prices and very knowledgeable in all things electrical\n\nTimely, friendly, courteous and work was done neatly","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Kwasniak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVX1n0KmO-p0oM5yJL_CV8SWRomdlPH4EibJJVU5dfSOHos8s0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent! On time, polite, got the job done fast, explained everything thoroughly, and cleaned up after. I couldn’t ask for someone better!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Heide Erica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjnIIYWiYfGY_qxEPPvrutxpVaPXasjYGHkO6x4jFnzEkv3NE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service!  Locally owned and operated, with attention to detail and reasonable pricing\n\nVery happy with our new exterior garage lamps","Im