e fixed it. The payment was super easy too, they send an electronic invoice with multiple ways to pay including Venmo and Apple Pay.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crittle D.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKH3LZH2qdH7EiadWZdG3ByYGK3efgYQra83lE4RXfD-yKvQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a refreshing experience I had with Cody and All Communities Electric! The price was very reasonable, considerably less than other estimates I received. Cody obviously knew what he was doing and completed the electric for a mini split quickly. Everything looked good and was clean and tidy when he finished. I would trust him to do further electric jobs for me in a heartbeat.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darren Learmonth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnO3X9kvRw5AiuE1v1XHRBSkgaqEHxyj6xQJJATI4eJ_QIvZso=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cody promptly gave me a great estimate, suggested how I could save some money, and then delivered quality timely work, with humor and professionalism. Don’t hesitate get Cody to help with your electrical needs","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQLHqBkJkkYhxnswRF2A4jSJ1fC2l9JUyAPPkeEJgWMdxxkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cody is the BEST!  He took care of business immediately with same day service to install my Tesla charger!  Absolute perfect and promptness. He communicated throughout the process to ensure the higher quality and customer satisfaction.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Schelina J.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJavIUe-iwvVD2nozpraE6SxfX7uQ43HjVnxrF52qYROtaYBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this company! They are extremely responsive and great at repairs and installation. Cody is a genuinely nice person who arrives on time and keeps his word. I did a lot of comparison shopping and their pricing is better than the other providers in the Bastrop area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Youngerman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjR8MKB9tvjMZMXCkjOWtK7JcQzqqDJlvUfjKuZWeOSTKvB9ul=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All Communities Electric did a phenomenal job on my requested work. Cody is punctual, professional and an expert in his field!! I highly recommend them and will use them again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ethan Horne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0-8mpBJ8BXZC6p7teumDUyjxLcg1MbsBSPbkb9XvixZ9DvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don was great to work with.  We were having an HVAC system put in a home.  I worked with someone else who didn't quite get what I needed.  Don sent someone the same day, explained I didn't need a bigger panel, but explained how to get the best use out of what I had.  He gave me a good price, and was fast.  I should point out he asked if I had detailed pictures of the electrical panel, which I did.  He was able to understand my needs better because I sent him clear detailed pictures.  That was important to him.  Thank you Don.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
