 our office.  Trent was thorough, focused, and a good listener.  The team was very knowledgeable, quick, and efficient.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annie Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLnXuJ8OjQBmsItgj48GkYTi1wW0GBBCn9A8qDC02SGCGeEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I decided to use Chapman electric because several people in a Lakeway Facebook group had recommended them. I am so glad that I ended up having them come and do the work I needed done. I had two rather heavy medieval looking chandeliers that were installed when my home was built that I had always wanted to take down and have replaced with something more modern. Not only did they show up early but they were able to take down these two chandeliers and install the two new ones in about 30 or 40 minutes. They were so friendly and informative and kept a very clean careful workspace. I also just had my floors redone so I was a little nervous about whether they would take the right kind of caution in protecting this very expensive asset. They did a phenomenal job. They also moved my old chandeliers into a space where I planned to store them. All in all I would give them a five star rating. I absolutely plan to use them again if I have other electrician needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Clemons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSgtpNTLasgoF856wBbwxZJ_tBFCERoLNI1yCtMN2XK-QiOQWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience with Chapman Electric was exceptional. My electrician was very efficient and provided a great service for a decent price. I highly recommend this company for anyone looking for electrical work.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn01AkEw_9kZcH9wrjgl3ZGffpX4DHlK_E-ugPOujBoRW-HCWNrCyp-7SioH56aPVJUtLDReCyR-6BLnzjXRVEn6ztAj0UEdrfq_MbbTqOVaYm8xPoZhs0UA1He2mdh4JcisII_qOQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Amanda H (The Traveling Grits)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1zRMgdXRru9qBHMdDIKwyjPayzYfTgMtrqNtNmyVnW-I7aYM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chapman Electric has been, by far, one of the best contractors we’ve worked with after the purchase of our new home. They have been communicative, responsive, prompt and efficient every step of the way. From the initial consult, to the streamlined quoting and booking process to the perfectly prompt and efficient electricians they sent out- every step of the way has been easy and efficient.They even completed the scope of work quicker than expected and adjusted the invoice accordingly. Cannot recommend enough and they will be our go-to electricians going forward. Above and beyond experience from start to finish. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Stoltman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlFdk8TLEUxbze5TESFozVtDUQ4m0xhSkHT1xtzTjPLn04sUJiSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have used Chapman twice to help upgrade the lighting in our house; the first in 2022 when they replaced all our light cans with LED wafers and updated all of the fans, undercounter, bathroom, and hanging light fixtures.  They also installed upgraded exterior floods.  They recently came back and we had them add above cabinet lighting in the kitchen and LED ceiling lights in 4 rooms that previously only had ceiling fan lights.  They also troubleshooted a few issues for us.  They always do a fantastic job - on time, on schedule, great quality and great team members!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Meyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFF9mRFyIHu41auO_brRtwCbEzof8l663hR8WTAxAWLLajBB2z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chuck and his team nailed it! They arrived on time, did a fantastic job setting up the electric for my new Jacuzzi, and upgrading my electrical panel. I'm over the moon with their work and would absolutely recommend them without any doubt.","I