g be done in a timely manner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Schley Barrack","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILMir45QFJ-gh-i_wz6sZOgYaewnN-MhpSuB_OGVOV6jmZeg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guys were cheaper than some other quotes that I got, were responsive and easy to get in touch with, and came out and did a great job putting in a 30 amp plug at our place!  Will definitely be contacting them again with any further work we might need","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
