r them to anyone that needs electrical work done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryo Inoue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqeGm8ucqdUWET7o4-FHmUNZxU4uAfGm7Gcw2lPbpVu96kIUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been a customer of ACE Electric for 5 years, first with Carl and now with DJ and Eden. Very friendly and professional. They explain the cause of the problems in great detail and the work is done quickly and at a very reasonable price. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kenneth Gore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYjx5SB4ocICCHjh26fOA5OVtmunGvd0_qBuWTKq2yqp29bg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife got the referral from a friend.  We are so happy we went with DJ and his team.  They were knowledgeable and efficient with quality installation of 4 outlets and 3 ceiling fans/lights. True professionals in their craft.  My wife had many questions about future projects and Eden provided detailed information on all her questions. Will be using Ace Electric for all our electrical needs in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Artusi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrneMxGXBoQtB1fs3vJh6V7Dp51IUei2qPmY_XHYRL_2IBLQd4tw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This company is amazing because of their amazing team. I couldn't be more pleased with their work. I needed to install a 240V outlet in my garage to plug a Level 2 charger for an EV and it was not a trivial installation because the main panel is located on the other side of the house. The team was awesome at routing the large gauge wires through the attic and installing the outlet in an ideal location where I can reach the charging port of the car.\nThey were super competent, skilled, friendly and fast. I was delighted by their work and interactions.\nI'd recommend DJ and his team without hesitation for any electrical work.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36DMSnC4HcI7QgXZBy9Ou5sEHOkr1_PC4GrMyvg0CGpRhr9HIi6kZ5I04EeXEawUmm4i8qm9ijMzOeXxwNnCaSrAz36obr-HH8Yd3UHznVikSieZoOED78laVRlT9ODo2rreUxmw=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-25"},{"Name":"Chris Gaston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCQ8c6cqDy501i8hAQKs71bejcH09uVDpNE6pB39aM-DRSLg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mr. Daniel George has been very helpful on multiple occasions. He is very communicative and provides great service. We highly recommend Ace Electric!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Shaw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGPAL9GVnH8o_74ZL4SXEbt4Sfkc94SpM4-rMz6_Yvt8-Z0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Ace electric. I had them out to add more lighting in my backyard since it's my favorite place and I spend many hours out there. They came on time and did the job quickly and efficiently. I felt bad that Eden had to go into the attic in the Texas heat, but he said it wasn't bad. Thanks to DJ and his staff for a job well done! I will use Ace for any future electrical work that might pop up as they proved to be honest, did an outstanding job and didn't break the bank with their pricing. Look no further than Ace Electric when you're in need of excellent service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheryl/Grant Halter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCg_1Ja5ZNTBbRlnKOFLMKMeWm7CN2pUnYhTd6P5HtpZ-eog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"D.J. did a great job and was very pleasant to deal with.\nI plan to use ACE ELECTRIC again.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
